From 50c9d14805d52914bb346644f553b5e137da96eb Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Work Leaf Bench <bench@example.com>
Date: Wed, 10 Jun 2026 21:24:05 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] ADD vim-style visual selection for terminal pane copying

Track visual character, line, and block selections inside the terminal UI state machine so focused left and right panes can use vim-style v, V, Ctrl-V, y, and Y copy workflows without involving backend prompts.
---
